    ('B', 'Processing delay; Incomplete details/documents; System validation checks', 'Verify details entered; Check status/notifications; Retry after some time', 'Retry after verifying inputs; Provide reference IDs to support if needed', 'As applicable (only if requested by support).', 'Typically 24-72 working hours depending on third-party processing (bank/AMC/broker/insurer).'),
    ('C', 'Request needs verification; Mismatch with KYC records; Incomplete supporting proof', 'Ensure details match KYC; Prepare required proof; Check if joint holders need consent', 'Submit request with supporting documents; Track status; Raise ticket if beyond timeline', 'Signed request (if needed); Relevant proof (bank/addr/contact)', 'Typically 24-72 working hours depending on third-party processing (bank/AMC/broker/insurer).'),
