    ('E', 'Settlement timeline not completed; Cutoff/holiday; Bank details mismatch', 'Check transaction date/cutoff; Confirm bank details; Check statement', 'Wait for settlement; Raise ticket with folio/order ID if exceeded; We coordinate with AMC/bank', 'As applicable (only if requested by support).', 'Typically 24-72 working hours depending on third-party processing (bank/AMC/broker/insurer).'),
    ('F', 'Network/DND settings; SMS gateway delay; Incorrect registered mobile', 'Verify registered mobile; Check DND/network; Retry after 2-5 minutes', 'Retry OTP; Try login again; Raise ticket with time/screenshot if persists', 'Screenshot (optional)', 'Usually within minutes; investigate if persists beyond 30 minutes.'),
    ('G', 'Incorrect credentials; Account locked; Cache/app issue', 'Try password reset; Check caps lock; Try another device/browser', 'Reset password; Clear cache/reinstall; Contact support if locked', 'As applicable (only if requested by support).', 'Typically 24-72 working hours depending on third-party processing (bank/AMC/broker/insurer).'),
    ('H', 'Mandate pending/expired; Insufficient balance; Bank processing failure', 'Check mandate status; Check balance; Check bank decline reason', 'Approve/renew mandate; Maintain balance; Retry next cycle', 'As applicable (only if requested by support).', 'Typically 24-72 working hours depending on third-party processing (bank/AMC/broker/insurer).')
